      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im a type 1 diabetic and i just finished a workout but im feeling really weird. im super shaky and sweaty and my head feels kind of fuzzy like im confused or something. i dont know if my sugar is too high or too low right now because i forgot my meter at home... should i just take a bit more insulin to try and level things out before it gets worse?",
