      "content": "wait but if it is high insulin is the only way to fix it... i feel like my blood is gonna be super thick if it's high. if i wait and it turns out it was actually high the juice will just make it way worse and dangerous right? i feel like i should just do a small correction dose now just to be safe and call it an even playing field.",
